      <title>特朗普和哈里斯在辩论中就经济计划发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-11/trump-and-harris-clash-over-economic-plans-in-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯在 ABC 新闻总统辩论中就各自的经济计划发生冲突。特朗普表示，他与“2025 计划”无关，他将大幅减税。哈里斯指出，高盛的一份报告称，特朗普的计划将使经济恶化。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-11/trump-and-harris-clash-over-economic-plans-in-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 03:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济放缓担忧加剧，全球债券收益率跌至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/global-bond-yields-drop-to-two-year-low-as-slowdown-fears-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对主要经济体增长放缓的担忧和降息预期升温，本周全球债券收益率跌至两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/global-bond-yields-drop-to-two-year-low-as-slowdown-fears-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 02:31:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
