    <item>
      <title>日本央行官员讲话后日元升至 1 月 2 日以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/yen-gains-to-strongest-since-jan-2-after-boj-official-speaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行一位委员暗示如果日元价格和经济前景得到满足，未来仍会加息之后，日元兑美元升至今年初以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/yen-gains-to-strongest-since-jan-2-after-boj-official-speaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯与支持加密货币的特朗普在辩论中发生冲突，比特币价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员对美国总统候选人民主党卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 与共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 之间的辩论做出反应，比特币出现下滑，而特朗普对加密货币领域十分感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特称，澳大利亚央行对就业指标的有限放松感到“意外”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/rba-surprised-by-limited-easing-in-job-gauges-hunter-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行助理行长萨拉·亨特 (Sarah Hunter) 表示，今年一些关键就业指标的“有限”放松令央行感到惊讶，这强化了央行关于劳动力市场仍然超负荷运转的观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/rba-surprised-by-limited-easing-in-job-gauges-hunter-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 00:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧加剧油价跌势，油价稳定在 70 美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球需求的担忧迅速升级，引发了油价迅速而强劲的抛售，导致布伦特原油价格两年多来首次跌破每桶 70 美元，随后油价趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 23:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员消化美国辩论，股市下跌，日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三亚洲股市下跌，原因是美国通胀报告公布前市场对经济增长的担忧，以及交易员权衡总统辩论的影响。日本央行官员暗示将进一步加息，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 22:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国不可行的房地产救助方案正在延长危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/china-s-unworkable-housing-rescue-math-is-prolonging-the-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年 5 月，中国中央政府要求 200 多个城市收购滞销房屋，以缓解供应过剩问题。三个多月后，只有 29 个城市响应了这一号召。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/china-s-unworkable-housing-rescue-math-is-prolonging-the-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
